file.name: priority.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  title: Adzerk Management API - Priorities
  description: Priority related Adzerk Management API
  version: '1.0'
servers:
  - url: 'https://api.adzerk.net'
tags:
  - name: priority
    description: Manage Priorities
paths:
  /v1/priority:
    post:
      tags:
        - priority
      operationId: create
      security:
        - ApiKeyAuth: []
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              type: object
              required:
                - Name
                - ChannelID
                - Weight
                - SelectionAlgorithm
              properties:
                Name:
                  type: string
                ChannelID:
                  type: string
                Weight:
                  type: integer
                  format: int32
                  minimum: 1
                  maximum: 100
                SelectionAlgorithm:
                  type: integer
                  format: int32
                  enum: [0, 1, 2, 3, 4]
                IsDeleted:
                  type: boolean
                  nullable: true
                IsKeywordOptimized:
                  type: boolean
                  nullable: true
                FloorPrice:
                  type: number
                  format: float
                  nullable: true
                IsSecondPricing:
                  type: boolean
                  nullable: true
                PassbackTimeout:
                  type: integer
                  format: int32
                  nullable: true
      responses:
        200:
          description: The newly created priority
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: './schemas/priority.yaml#/schemas/Priority'
    get:
      tags:
        - priority
      operationId: list
      security:
        - ApiKeyAuth: []
      parameters:
        - name: pageSize
          in: query
          description: The size of the page to be returned
          required: false
          schema:
            type: integer
            format: int32
            nullable: true
            default: 500
        - name: page
          in: query
          description: The page number to be returned
          required: false
          schema:
            type: integer
            format: int32
            nullable: true
      responses:
        200:
          description: A paged list of the Priorities
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: './schemas/priority.yaml#/schemas/PriorityList'
  '/v1/priority/{id}':
    parameters:
      - name: id
        in: path
        description: The Channel Id
        required: true
        schema:
          type: integer
          format: int32
    get:
      tags:
        - priority
      operationId: get
      security:
        - ApiKeyAuth: []
      responses:
        200:
          description: The Priority
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: './schemas/priority.yaml#/schemas/Priority'
    put:
      tags:
        - priority
      operationId: update
      security:
        - ApiKeyAuth: []
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              type: object
              required:
                - Id
                - Name
                - ChannelID
                - Weight
              properties:
                Id:
                  type: integer
                  format: int32
                Name:
                  type: string
                ChannelID:
                  type: string
                Weight:
                  type: integer
                  format: int32
                  minimum: 1
                  maximum: 100
                IsDeleted:
                  type: boolean
                  nullable: true
                FloorPrice:
                  type: number
                  format: float
                  nullable: true
                IsSecondPricing:
                  type: boolean
                  nullable: true
                PassbackTimeout:
                  type: boolean
                  nullable: true
      responses:
        200:
          description: The updated priority
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: './schemas/priority.yaml#/schemas/Priority'
  '/v1/priority/{id}/delete':
    get:
      tags:
        - priority
      operationId: delete
      security:
        - ApiKeyAuth: []
      parameters:
        - name: id
          in: path
          description: The Channel Id
          required: true
          schema:
            type: integer
            format: int32
      responses:
        200:
          description: Successfully Deleted
components:
  securitySchemes:
    $ref: './components/security-schemes.yaml#/components/securitySchemes'
